.header
  = render "/layouts/header"
.breadcrumbs
  = render "/layouts/breadcrumbs"
.interviewsform
  .interviewsform__in
    %ul
      %li
        %h1
          1.今回病院にかかられた症状、診断名が分かればご入力ください。
        %input.interviewsform__in__diagnosis{:placeholder => "例）鼻水が出る、熱っぽい、過敏性大腸炎", :type => "text"}
      %li
        %h1
          2.薬で副作用が起きたことがありますか？
          %br/
          薬の名前
        %input.interviewsform__in__se_medicine{:placeholder => "例）クラビット", :type => "text"}
        %h1
          症状
        %input.interviewsform__in__se_symptom{:placeholder => "例）お腹を下したことがあります", :type => "text"}
      %li
        %h1
          3.現在、他の医療機関で治療中の病気はありますか？
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :medical_history1
          =label_tag :medical_history1, "高血圧"
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :medical_history2
          =label_tag :medical_history2, "心臓疾患"
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :medical_history3
          =label_tag :medical_history3, "脳梗塞"
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :medical_history4
          =label_tag :medical_history4, "脂質異常症"
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :medical_history5
          =label_tag :medical_history5, "糖尿病"
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :medical_history6
          =label_tag :medical_history6, "肝臓病"
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :medical_history7
          =label_tag :medical_history7, "腎臓病"
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :medical_history8
          =label_tag :medical_history8, "緑内障"
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :medical_history9
          =label_tag :medical_history9, "前立腺疾患"
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :medical_history10
          =label_tag :medical_history10, "甲状腺疾患"
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :medical_history11
          =label_tag :medical_history11, "胃・十二指腸潰瘍"
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :medical_history12
          =label_tag :medical_history12, "リウマチ"
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :medical_history13
          =label_tag :medical_history13, "骨粗しょう症"
        %input.interviewsform__in__medical_history{:placeholder => "その他あれば入力してください", :type => "text"}
      %li
        %h1
          5.お薬手帳に記載してあるもの以外に、現在服用している薬やサプリメントはありますか？
        %input.profilesform__in__sex{:placeholder => "例）女性・男性・回答しない", :type => "text"}
      %li
        %h1
          6.自動車運転など、生活に当てはまるものがあれば教えてください。
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :life_details1
          =label_tag :life_details1, "自動車の運転をする"
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :life_details2
          =label_tag :life_details2, "視力をよく使う"
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :life_details3
          =label_tag :life_details3, "高所など危険な場所での仕事をする"
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :life_details4
          =label_tag :life_details4, "夜勤などで不規則"
      %li
        %h1
          7.お酒は飲みますか？
          %br/
          %input.interviewsform__in__drinking{:name => "drinking", :id =>"drinking1", :type => "radio"}
          =label_tag :drinking1, "よく飲む"
          %input.interviewsform__in__drinking{:name => "drinking", :id =>"drinking2", :type => "radio"}
          =label_tag :drinking2, "たまに飲む"
          %input.interviewsform__in__drinking{:name => "drinking", :id =>"drinking3", :type => "radio"}
          =label_tag :drinking3, "全く飲まない"
      %li
        %h1
          8.タバコは吸いますか？
          %br/
          %input.interviewsform__in__smoking{:name => "smoking", :id =>"smoking1", :type => "radio"}
          =label_tag :smoking1, "よく吸う"
          %input.interviewsform__in__smoking{:name => "smoking", :id =>"smoking2", :type => "radio"}
          =label_tag :smoking2, "たまに吸う"
          %input.interviewsform__in__smoking{:name => "smoking", :id =>"smoking3", :type => "radio"}
          =label_tag :smoking3, "全く吸わない"
      %li
        %h1
          9.飲めない形の薬があれば教えてください
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :dosage_form1
          =label_tag :dosage_form1, "粉薬"
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :dosage_form2
          =label_tag :dosage_form2, "錠剤"
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :dosage_form3
          =label_tag :dosage_form3, "カプセル"
          %br/
          =check_box_tag :dosage_form4
          =label_tag :dosage_form4, "水薬"
      %li
        %h1
          10.女性の方に伺います。妊娠中、または妊娠している可能性がありますか？
          %br/
          %input.interviewsform__in__pregnancy{:name => "pregnancy", :id =>"pregnancy1", :type => "radio"}
          =label_tag :pregnancy1, "はい"
          %input.interviewsform__in__pregnancy{:name => "pregnancy", :id =>"pregnancy2", :type => "radio"}
          =label_tag :pregnancy2, "いいえ"
      %li
        %h1
          11.女性の方に伺います。現在、授乳中ですか？
          %br/
          %input.interviewsform__in__breastfeeding{:name => "breastfeeding", :id =>"breastfeeding1", :type => "radio"}
          =label_tag :breastfeeding1, "はい"
          %input.interviewsform__in__breastfeeding{:name => "breastfeeding", :id =>"breastfeeding2", :type => "radio"}
          =label_tag :breastfeeding2, "いいえ"
      %li
        %h1
          12.小児（子ども）の方は、現在の体重を教えてください。
        %input.profilesform__in__telephone{:placeholder => "例）090-1234-5678", :type => "text"}
      %li
        %h1
          13.ジェネリック医薬品（後発品）に変更できる処方箋であった場合、変更を希望されますか？
          %span 必須
          %br/
          %input.interviewsform__in__generic{:name => "generic", :id =>"generic1", :type => "radio"}
          =label_tag :generic1, "はい"
          %input.interviewsform__in__generic{:name => "generic", :id =>"generic2", :type => "radio"}
          =label_tag :generic2, "いいえ"
      %li
        %br/
        %button.usersform__in__send{:name => "submit", :placeholder => "送信", :type => "submit"}
          回答を送信する